{"tid":882514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌2軍裝警蛇王斷正　網民：阿Sir瞓覺唔使你教！","createTime":"2018-10-30T07:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T04:50:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":271,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac457c3825401c9f69ea31b670eafeadfeb5f11","tid":882514,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181030/photo/bkn-20181030142724800-1030_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181030151500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181030142724800-1030_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181030151500&h=0de278ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名軍裝警員在警車上睡覺。(小心駕駛(討論別人態度)fb)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今時今日，竟然有紀律部隊人員公然在街上集體「瞓覺」蛇王，有網民在小心駕駛(討論別人態度)Facebook專頁上載圖片，顯示兩名軍裝警員正在警車上睡覺，其中一人戴上太陽眼鏡，另一人則沉沉大睡，雙雙進入夢鄉。 <br />\n<br />\n該名網民貼文表示，「阿Sir訓(瞓)覺，吾(唔)洗(使)你教呀」，據知，拍攝位置位於葵涌麗瑤邨東華三院高可寧紀念小學門外，地點頗為隱蔽。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，兩名軍裝警員駐守葵涌分區巡邏小隊，事發時正在當早更，事件令葵青警區管理層震怒，二人已被召回問話，將會被紀律處分。東網正向警方查詢。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181030/photo/bkn-20181030142724800-1030_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181030151500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181030142724800-1030_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181030151500&h=55fcd1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片拍攝於葵涌麗瑤邨東華三院高可寧紀念小學門外。(小心駕駛(討論別人態度)fb)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181030/bkn-20181030142724800-1030_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181030%2Fbkn-20181030142724800-1030_00822_001.html&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ec2d893f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181030/bkn-20181030142724800-1030_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bd57654e85643f0aaa63bc10b0a804d472ee5f37","tid":882514,"uid":95542,"like":347,"dislike":4,"score":343,"citedBy":4,"replyT